==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''[[piece]] of [[furniture]]''' (''plural'' '''pieces of furniture''')

# Any item, such as a table or cupboard, that consistutes furniture.

====Usage notes====
'''Piece of furniture''' is used as a singular of the [[mass noun]] '''[[furniture]]''', which has no singular of its own.

